      "author": "VIktor (Viktor)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello together,</p>\n<p>is it possible to clear the date column of a subitem. I tried it with the “item_id” it works fine. But when I use the “subitem_id”. I get an error: “Item not found in board.”</p>\n<p>Best Regards<br />\nViktor</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/5/25c20c400e0004b24a7005ccd04c2700958b8bb2.png\" title=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-07-20 um 10.33.34\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/5/25c20c400e0004b24a7005ccd04c2700958b8bb2_2_690x373.png\" alt=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-07-20 um 10.33.34\" width=\"690\" height=\"373\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Bildschirmfoto 2024-07-20 um 10.33.34</span><span class=\"informations\">2976×1612 327 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/9/296f5a827011e9986a632e56526c9df172252607.png\" title=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-07-20 um 10.42.43\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/9/296f5a827011e9986a632e56526c9df172252607_2_690x339.png\" alt=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-07-20 um 10.42.43\" width=\"690\" height=\"339\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Bildschirmfoto 2024-07-20 um 10.42.43</span><span class=\"informations\">3000×1476 348 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/0/404a614c13ca21e1de8e393db61430161a606fe8.png\" title=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-07-20 um 10.33.10\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/0/404a614c13ca21e1de8e393db61430161a606fe8_2_690x339.png\" alt=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-07-20 um 10.33.10\" width=\"690\" height=\"339\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Bildschirmfoto 2024-07-20 um 10.33.10</span><span class=\"informations\">3020×1484 349 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
